; organ downloads each hash-pinned file to a neutral numeric name, gives only
; those samples to Whisper (no prompt), then gives only Whisper's transcript
; and locale to the complete 10,000-concept Form detector.
; witnessed: 2026-07-18 -> 13 source rows, 13 locales, 13 speakers, 13 concepts
; preludes: form/form-stdlib/core.fk

